<title>lián mǐn wǒ zhōng huá zhǔ 迦南195</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lián mǐn wǒ zhōng huá zhǔ, shōu huí nǐ de nù qì,
 lián mǐn wǒ zhōng huá zhǔ, shōu huí nǐ de nù qì,
 wǒ men qí qiú nǐ zhǔ lián mǐn wǒ zhōng huá,
